## 📝 CHANGELOG.md FORMAT

**File: `CHANGELOG.md`**

```markdown
# Changelog

All notable changes to DevFlow Pro will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- Upcoming features in development

## [1.2.0] - 2026-04-10

### Added
- 🔄 Auto-update system with version detection
- 📥 One-click update installation
- 🔙 Rollback to previous version
- 📊 Changelog viewer in-app
- 🔔 Smart update notifications

### Changed
- Improved MySQL connection pooling
- Updated dependencies to latest versions

### Fixed
- Memory leak in bug fetcher (#42)
- Git commit message formatting (#38)
- Status bar flickering on update check

### Breaking Changes
- None

## [1.1.0] - 2026-03-25

### Added
- GitHub Issues integration
- Webhook notifications (Slack/Discord)
- Export CSV/JSON functionality

### Fixed
- Bug in auto-fix workflow (#27)

## [1.0.0] - 2026-03-10

### Added
- Initial release
- MySQL database integration
- GitHub Copilot code generation
- Automatic Git commits
- Bug dashboard UI

[Unreleased]: https://github.com/phoenixdepot/devflow-pro/compare/v1.2.0...HEAD
[1.2.0]: https://github.com/phoenixdepot/devflow-pro/compare/v1.1.0...v1.2.0
[1.1.0]: https://github.com/phoenixdepot/devflow-pro/compare/v1.0.0...v1.1.0
[1.0.0]: https://github.com/phoenixdepot/devflow-pro/releases/tag/v1.0.0
```

