## 🚀 DEPLOYMENT WORKFLOW

### Script de publication automatique:

**File: `scripts/publish-update.sh`**

```bash
#!/bin/bash

# DevFlow Pro - Update Publisher
# Usage: ./scripts/publish-update.sh 1.2.0 "Bug fixes and improvements"

VERSION=$1
MESSAGE=$2
CHANNEL=${3:-stable} # stable or beta

if [ -z "$VERSION" ] || [ -z "$MESSAGE" ]; then
  echo "Usage: ./publish-update.sh <version> <message> [channel]"
  echo "Example: ./publish-update.sh 1.2.0 'Bug fixes' stable"
  exit 1
fi

echo "🚀 Publishing DevFlow Pro v$VERSION ($CHANNEL)"

# 1. Update package.json version
echo "📝 Updating version..."
npm version $VERSION --no-git-tag-version

# 2. Build extension
echo "🔨 Building extension..."
npm run compile

# 3. Package .vsix
echo "📦 Packaging .vsix..."
vsce package

# 4. Calculate SHA256
VSIX_FILE="devflow-pro-$VERSION.vsix"
SHA256=$(shasum -a 256 $VSIX_FILE | awk '{print $1}')
SIZE=$(stat -f%z $VSIX_FILE)

echo "📊 File hash: $SHA256"
echo "📊 File size: $SIZE bytes"

# 5. Upload to server (example using scp)
echo "☁️  Uploading to server..."
scp $VSIX_FILE user@phoenixdepot.com:/var/www/devflow/downloads/

# 6. Update manifest.json
echo "📄 Updating manifest..."
cat > manifest-$CHANNEL.json << EOF
{
  "version": "$VERSION",
  "downloadUrl": "https://phoenixdepot.com/devflow/downloads/$VSIX_FILE",
  "releaseDate": "$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)",
  "changelog": "$MESSAGE",
  "minVSCodeVersion": "^1.85.0",
  "breaking": false,
  "sha256": "$SHA256",
  "size": $SIZE
}
EOF

scp manifest-$CHANNEL.json user@phoenixdepot.com:/var/www/devflow/updates/$CHANNEL/manifest.json

# 7. Git commit & tag
echo "🏷️  Creating git tag..."
git add .
git commit -m "Release v$VERSION"
git tag "v$VERSION"
git push origin main --tags

# 8. Create GitHub release (if using GitHub)
if command -v gh &> /dev/null; then
  echo "🐙 Creating GitHub release..."
  gh release create "v$VERSION" \
    --title "v$VERSION" \
    --notes "$MESSAGE" \
    $VSIX_FILE
fi

echo "✅ Done! Version $VERSION published to $CHANNEL channel"
echo "🔗 Download: https://phoenixdepot.com/devflow/downloads/$VSIX_FILE"
```

**Usage:**
```bash
chmod +x scripts/publish-update.sh
./scripts/publish-update.sh 1.2.0 "Added auto-update system" stable
```

